<span id="freeTextContainer10905070882610590645">An absolutely stunning debut; one of the best I&apos;ve read. Yaa Gyasi captures so many stories and handles them beautifully. We need more novels like this. And it&apos;s only her first! I can&apos;t wait to see what she does next.</span>
  <span id="freeText10905070882610590645" style="display:none">An absolutely stunning debut; one of the best I've read. Yaa Gyasi captures so many stories and handles them beautifully. We need more novels like this. And it's only her first! I can't wait to see what she does next.</span>
